<doc id="390500" wikidata="Q2231898" url="?curid=390500" title="Arturo Michelena International Airport">
<text>Arturo Michelena International Airport is an airport serving the city of Valencia in Venezuela. The airport was named after artist Arturo Michelena, who was born in Valencia. It is a hub for Turpial Airlines and was once a secondary hub for Avior Airlines.

