===Gallery===

==Directors==
Jennifer Scott became Director of Dulwich Picture Gallery in April 2017, following Ian A.C. Dejardin who had been director since 2005. From 1996 to 2005, Desmond Shawe-Taylor, later Surveyor of the Queen&#x27;s Pictures, was the Director. Giles Waterfield was Director of the Dulwich Picture Gallery from 1979-1996.

